OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FA British widow said she had to bury
OL,7,Fher husband in an unmarked grave in
OL,8,FCape Verde after he fell ill and died
OL,9,Fthere while on holiday.
OL,11,FLaw firm Irwin Mitchell said it now
OL,12,Frepresents more than 2,500 people who
OL,13,Fhave complained of illnesses ` such as
OL,14,Fsalmonella, E.coli and shigella `
OL,15,Fafter holidays in the West African
OL,16,Fcountry since the summer of 2022.
OL,18,FAmong them are the families of 10
OL,19,Fpeople who died of gastric illnesses
OL,20,Fwhile on holidays booked through Tui,
OL,21,Fthe law firm said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FThey are all planning legal action
OL,7,Fagainst the travel company.
OL,9,FRetired forklift driver Colin Timson,
OL,10,F74, from Heighington, near Lincoln,
OL,11,Ffell ill on the second day of his
OL,12,F#2,000 two-week stay at the Riu Funana
OL,13,Fresort in Sal in July 2024.
OL,15,FHis wife Jacqueline Timson, 69, said
OL,16,Fthat she found him collapsed the next
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FMr Timson died in hospital later that
OL,7,Fevening and a death certificate from
OL,8,Fthe Cape Verde authorities said his
OL,9,Fcause of death was dehydration, severe
OL,10,Fanaemia and septic shock caused by
OL,11,Facute gastroenteritis and digestive
OL,12,Fbleeding, the law firm said.
OL,14,FMrs Timson, who also fell ill, said
OL,15,Fshe had to bury her husband in an
OL,16,Funmarked grave three days after his
OL,17,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FShe said: "We'd been to Cape Verde
OL,7,Fbefore and were looking forward to
OL,8,Freturning. However, when we arrived at
OL,9,Fthe hotel we didn't feel it was the
OL,10,Fsame standard we'd found on our
OL,11,Fprevious holiday to Cape Verde.
OL,13,F"Some of the food appeared to be
OL,14,Fundercooked and was lukewarm. The
OL,15,Ftoilets around the pool were full of
OL,16,Fdead cockroaches and we didn't go in
OL,17,Fthe pool because the water looked
OL,18,Fyellow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FMrs Timson said both she and Mr Timson
OL,7,Ffell ill at the same time, but he had
OL,8,Fit worse and was "vomiting yellow
OL,9,Fsick".
OL,11,FAfter he was sent to hospital, Mrs
OL,12,FTimpson said she had returned to the
OL,13,Fhotel as she was told he "would be in
OL,14,Fsafe hands."
OL,16,F"I didn't even know he'd died until I
OL,17,Farrived at the hospital the following
OL,18,Fday. When I heard the news my world
OL,19,Ffell apart," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,F"Everything was a blur, but I believed
OL,7,FI didn't have adequate travel
OL,8,Finsurance, and I thought it would have
OL,9,Fbeen too expensive to fly Colin home.
OL,11,F"I was told that there wasn't an
OL,12,Foption to have a cremation in Cape
OL,13,FVerde so I had to watch helplessly as
OL,14,Fhe was buried."
OL,16,FThe retired factory worker added: "I
OL,17,Fstill can't comprehend how we went on
OL,18,Fholiday together but Colin never came
OL,19,Fhome.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,F"The hardest thing is that I couldn't
OL,7,Feven bring his ashes home to be
OL,8,Falongside me. Instead, he's buried in
OL,9,Fan unmarked grave, alone, thousands of
OL,10,Fmiles away from his family."
OL,12,FIn June 2024, Laurence Brownlie, 67, a
OL,13,Fretired IT engineer from West Calder
OL,14,Fin West Lothian, Scotland, went to the
OL,15,Ffive-star Melia Llana Beach Resort and
OL,16,FSpa in Cape Verde with his wife,
OL,17,FGlenna, 66, for a two-week holiday
OL,18,Fwhen he became unwell.
OL,26,@wD@Orp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FThree days later, Mr Brownlie
OL,7,Fcollapsed at a dinner table and later
OL,8,Fdied, with a death certificate issued
OL,9,Fby the Cape Verde authorities saying
OL,10,Fthe cause of death was a suspected
OL,11,Fheart attack.
OL,13,FHis family have concerns about
OL,14,Fconditions at the resort, including
OL,15,Freports of flies in food and the
OL,16,Fabsence of a defibrillator, the law
OL,17,Ffirm said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FHis daughter Erin, 34, said: "It
OL,7,Fremains difficult not to think how dad
OL,8,Fshould have been coming home with mum
OL,9,Fat the end of their holiday.
OL,11,F"Instead, our family was left
OL,12,Fdevastated and trying to come to terms
OL,13,Fwith losing him so suddenly in such
OL,14,Ftraumatic circumstances.
OL,16,F"I can't imagine how harrowing it must
OL,17,Fhave been for my mum seeing her
OL,18,Fsoulmate pass away in front of her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,F"We'll forever be grateful to those in
OL,7,Fthe hotel who tried to help dad but
OL,8,Fwhat happened has left us with so many
OL,9,Funanswered questions. Nothing will
OL,10,Fever take away the pain of knowing he
OL,11,Fdied so far from home.
OL,13,F"As well as grieving for dad, we had
OL,14,Fto deal with the shock of flying out
OL,15,Fto be with mum, not being able to see
OL,16,Fhim, and then facing the journey of
OL,17,Fbringing him back to Scotland.
OL,19,F"It's something no family should ever
OL,20,Fhave to go through."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FMelia Hotels & Resorts have all been
OL,7,Fapproached for comment.
OL,9,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for Tui
OL,15,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with both
OL,16,Ffamilies. As we would for any family
OL,17,Ffacing a serious incident or
OL,18,Fbereavement while travelling with us,
OL,19,FTui's local representatives offered
OL,20,Fsupport and assistance in resort at
OL,21,Fthe time.
OL,26,@nD@Erp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,F"Neither family raised any complaint
OL,7,For concern with Tui, either during
OL,8,Ftheir holiday or after returning home,
OL,9,Fand Tui received no communication
OL,10,Fabout either case until today, when we
OL,11,Fwere contacted by media. As this is
OL,12,Fnow a legal matter, it would not be
OL,13,Fappropriate for us to comment further."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for RIU Hotels &
OL,16,FResorts said: "First and foremost, all
OL,17,Fof us at RIU Hotels & Resorts deeply
OL,18,Fregret the loss of these families and
OL,19,Four thoughts remain with them, as we
OL,20,Fwould with any guest that may face a
OL,21,Fserious incident when staying with us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,F"Out of respect for our guests'
OL,7,Fprivacy and in compliance with data
OL,8,Fprotection regulations, we cannot
OL,9,Fprovide information regarding specific
OL,10,Fpersonal cases. Furthermore, as this
OL,11,Fis now a legal matter, we are unable
OL,12,Fto comment further."
OL,14,FJatinder Paul, serious injury lawyer
OL,15,Fat Irwin Mitchell, said: "It's
OL,16,Fstaggering that we continue to be
OL,17,Fcontacted by hundreds more people
OL,18,Freporting how their holidays have been
OL,19,Fruined by serious illness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,F"Nothing brings the impact of these
OL,7,Fincidents into sharper focus than the
OL,8,Fdeaths of British holidaymakers.
OL,10,F"The first-hand accounts from those
OL,11,Fwho have lost loved ones are not only
OL,12,Fincredibly stark but harrowing.
OL,14,F"Our focus is now on securing our
OL,15,Fclients the answers they deserve and,
OL,16,Fwhere needed, either the support they
OL,17,Frequire to come to terms with their
OL,18,Floss or the specialist rehabilitation
OL,19,Fthey require to try and overcome the
OL,20,Fimpact of their illnesses the best
OL,21,Fthey can."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783725539
OL,3,CTourist buried in unmarked grave after
OL,4,Cfalling ill on Cape Verde holiday
OL,6,FShigella is a gastrointestinal bug
OL,7,Fthat can cause severe diarrhoea, fever
OL,8,Fand stomach cramps. It can be caught
OL,9,Ffrom contaminated food, water or
OL,10,Fsurfaces.
OL,12,FSalmonella is often caused by eating
OL,13,For handling contaminated food.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
